{"name": "somde", "metadata": {"name": "somde", "version": "0.1.8", "classifiers": [], "home_page": "https://github.com/WhirlFirst/somde", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "Algorithm for finding gene spatial pattern based on Gaussian process accelerated by SOM", "upload_time": 1616553463}, "documentation": ["# SOMDE ![pypi](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/somde)\nAlgorithm for finding gene spatial pattern based on Gaussian process accelerated by SOM\n\n## Install\n\n```bash\nconda install -c conda-forge somoclu\nconda install pandas\nconda install patsy\npip install somde\n```\n\n## Data\nSlide-seq data we used can be downloaded from SpatialDB website:\nhttp://www.spatialomics.org/SpatialDB/download.php\n\n## Tutorial\n\n\n### load data\n```python\ndf = pd.read_csv(dataname+'count.csv',sep=',',index_col=1)\ncorinfo = pd.read_csv(dataname+'idx.csv',sep=',',index_col=0)\ncorinfo[\"total_count\"]=df.sum(0)\nX=corinfo[['x','y']].values.astype(np.float32)\n```\nAfter data loading, we can generate a SOM on the tissue spatial domain.\n### build SOM\n```python\nfrom somde import SomNode\nsom = SomNode(X,20)\n```\nYou can use `som.view()` to visualize the distribution of all SOM nodes.\n\n### integrate data sites and expression\n```python\nndf,ninfo = som.mtx(df)\n```\n`mtx`function will generate pesudo gene expression and spatial data site information at reduced resolution.\n\n### normalize data and identify SVgenes\nSince we integrated the original count data, we need to normalize gene expression matrix in each `SomNode` object.\n```python\nnres = som.norm()\nresult, SVnum =som.run()\n```\nThe identification step is mainly based on the adjusted Gaussian Process, which was first proposed by [SpatialDE](https://github.com/Teichlab/SpatialDE).\nVisualization results can be found at https://github.com/WhirlFirst/somde/blob/master/slide_seq0819_11_SOM.ipynb"], "modules": [{"name": "somde", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "somde.SomNode", "xref": {"fqname": "somde.som.SomNode", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "setup", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "setup.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "setup.long_description", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "somde.som", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "somde.som.SomNode", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "somde.som.SomNode.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "X", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "k", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "homogeneous_codebook", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "somde.som.SomNode.reTrain", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "ep", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "somde.som.SomNode.viewIniCodebook", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "orisize", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "codesize", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "somde.som.SomNode.view", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "raw", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "c", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "line", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "somde.som.SomNode.mtx", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "df", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "alpha", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "somde.som.SomNode.norm", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": nul